294
00:13:09,240 --> 00:13:10,440
There is absolutely no conflict

295
00:13:10,559 --> 00:13:12,200
Young Master Huo is broad-minded

296
00:13:15,080 --> 00:13:17,159
I can't eat with the man who killed my father

297
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:23,840
I'm sorry

298
00:13:24,039 --> 00:13:24,960
My wife here

299
00:13:25,519 --> 00:13:26,759
Just has a bit of a temper

300
00:13:27,080 --> 00:13:28,600
Sometimes she even hits me

301
00:13:29,080 --> 00:13:30,480
I'll go teach her a lesson now

302
00:13:30,879 --> 00:13:32,000
You guys eat first

303
00:13:32,000 --> 00:13:32,639
You guys eat first

304
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:33,639
Stop

305
00:13:35,320 --> 00:13:38,000
Come, it's a small matter, doesn't affect anything

306
00:13:38,519 --> 00:13:39,200
Come, let's keep drinking

307
00:13:48,159 --> 00:13:49,519
You said you'd avenge my father

308
00:13:49,759 --> 00:13:51,000
The big battle is imminent

309
00:13:51,320 --> 00:13:52,200
We can't touch him

310
00:13:53,279 --> 00:13:54,360
Just endure it for a bit

311
00:13:55,039 --> 00:13:56,960
This vengeance will definitely be taken

312
00:13:57,240 --> 00:13:58,440
So you want to be partners with him

313
00:13:59,360 --> 00:14:00,879
I just found out too

314
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:02,399
That he joined Division Commander Chen

315
00:14:02,399 --> 00:14:03,799
I don't understand you people

316
00:14:04,320 --> 00:14:05,240
One moment you're fighting this one

317
00:14:05,240 --> 00:14:06,159
The next you're making peace with that one

318
00:14:06,200 --> 00:14:07,879
I only know he is my father's murderer

319
00:14:08,080 --> 00:14:08,799
If you are going to

320
00:14:08,799 --> 00:14:09,840
Eat at the same table with him again

321
00:14:09,840 --> 00:14:10,840
And you can still swallow it

322
00:14:12,440 --> 00:14:13,399
Then excuse me for not joining you

323
00:14:29,480 --> 00:14:30,120
Reporting.

324
00:14:31,360 --> 00:14:32,519
My shrew of a wife...

325
00:14:32,519 --> 00:14:33,799
...is too fierce.

326
00:14:34,360 --> 00:14:36,440
I apologize to the two commanders.

327
00:14:37,879 --> 00:14:38,519
I kneel.

328
00:14:44,240 --> 00:14:47,600
The Chen-Wei alliance must be solid as a rock.

329
00:14:47,960 --> 00:14:48,600
Well said.

330
00:14:49,320 --> 00:14:50,600
Then let's wish that our first battle...

331
00:14:51,120 --> 00:14:52,480
...is a victory from the start.

332
00:14:52,600 --> 00:14:54,600
Cheers.

333
00:15:04,799 --> 00:15:06,639
Since my Sworn Brother joined our army...

334
00:15:07,000 --> 00:15:08,799
...many able-bodied men came admiring your name.

335
00:15:08,919 --> 00:15:10,240
It allowed me to recover some strength.

336
00:15:10,600 --> 00:15:11,440
I really thank you.

337
00:15:11,519 --> 00:15:12,360
You're too kind.

338
00:15:12,879 --> 00:15:13,840
We are all family.

339
00:15:14,480 --> 00:15:16,279
Although they came for my name...

340
00:15:16,919 --> 00:15:18,480
...they are still your soldiers.

341
00:15:21,039 --> 00:15:22,200
Acting as the vanguard this time...

342
00:15:22,639 --> 00:15:23,720
...you take them with you.

343
00:15:24,039 --> 00:15:24,960
They all look up to you.

344
00:15:25,879 --> 00:15:26,720
They are loyal to you.

345
00:15:27,360 --> 00:15:30,000
These men haven't fought a proper battle.

346
00:15:30,399 --> 00:15:31,759
Should we send some experienced ones?

347
00:15:32,759 --> 00:15:33,600
What do you mean?

348
00:15:35,159 --> 00:15:36,320
Do you look down on Commander Fan?

349
00:15:39,120 --> 00:15:39,639
Sworn Brother.

350
00:15:40,279 --> 00:15:40,960
This time...

351
00:15:41,480 --> 00:15:42,440
...just let loose...

352
00:15:42,960 --> 00:15:43,799
...and go all out.

353
00:15:44,399 --> 00:15:46,200
I'll handle the logistics support for you.

354
00:15:46,840 --> 00:15:48,679
Rations, weapons, take whatever you want.

355
00:15:50,600 --> 00:15:51,360
Commander Wei.

356
00:15:52,360 --> 00:15:54,519
Those dry rations of yours are damp.

357
00:15:55,559 --> 00:15:57,120
It's normal in this weather.

358
00:15:57,679 --> 00:15:58,799
And you call yourselves a regular army?

359
00:15:59,320 --> 00:16:00,240
We all know...

360
00:16:00,440 --> 00:16:02,360
...rations are the top priority on the battlefield.

361
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:04,000
If the brothers aren't full...

362
00:16:04,159 --> 00:16:04,960
...how can they kill the enemy?

363
00:16:05,919 --> 00:16:06,559
You, Commander Wei...

364
00:16:06,559 --> 00:16:08,320
...surely understand this principle, right?

365
00:16:08,799 --> 00:16:09,559
What do you mean?

366
00:16:09,559 --> 00:16:10,679
What do you mean "what do I mean"?

367
00:16:10,799 --> 00:16:11,480
Are you being stingy?

368
00:16:11,480 --> 00:16:12,440
Give us something good to eat.

369
00:16:12,559 --> 00:16:13,679
You are going to fight a war.

370
00:16:13,759 --> 00:16:14,960
You're not going to a banquet.

371
00:16:15,480 --> 00:16:17,279
Don't you know your own weight?

372
00:16:17,559 --> 00:16:19,000
My weight? You come here.

373
00:16:20,120 --> 00:16:20,799
Come on, come on.

374
00:16:22,559 --> 00:16:23,399
About this matter...

375
00:16:23,919 --> 00:16:25,480
...maybe I was negligent.

376
00:16:28,799 --> 00:16:30,000
If it's damp, it's damp.

377
00:16:30,320 --> 00:16:31,159
Is it moldy?

378
00:16:31,600 --> 00:16:33,759
If it's not moldy, it can be eaten.

379
00:16:33,960 --> 00:16:35,320
Why be so delicate?

380
00:16:35,960 --> 00:16:38,519
Some gun barrels are crooked.

381
00:16:39,399 --> 00:16:40,159
Some guns...

382
00:16:40,720 --> 00:16:41,519
...jam.

383
00:16:42,159 --> 00:16:42,720
Commander.

384
00:16:43,240 --> 00:16:45,039
These are probably the rejects.

385
00:16:45,480 --> 00:16:47,080
Do you think being a regular army is easy?

386
00:16:47,559 --> 00:16:49,080
We aren't like some bandits...

387
00:16:49,279 --> 00:16:50,320
...robbing and looting.

388
00:16:50,320 --> 00:16:51,399
Money comes so easily.

389
00:16:51,639 --> 00:16:52,200
What do you mean?

390
00:16:52,200 --> 00:16:52,759
What are you saying?

391
00:16:52,759 --> 00:16:53,919
I don't act lawlessly.

392
00:16:54,000 --> 00:16:54,639
Who is a bandit?

393
00:16:54,639 --> 00:16:55,440
What's wrong with bandits?

394
00:16:55,519 --> 00:16:56,759
Bandits follow rules better than you do.

395
00:16:56,919 --> 00:16:57,639
And talk about honor.

396
00:16:59,759 --> 00:17:00,679
Can you pull the trigger or not?

397
00:17:01,120 --> 00:17:02,519
If it fires, that's enough.

398
00:17:06,759 --> 00:17:07,320
Sworn Brother.

399
00:17:08,600 --> 00:17:09,879
Among the three forces...

400
00:17:10,400 --> 00:17:11,319
...our army is the weakest.

401
00:17:12,480 --> 00:17:14,599
This alliance with Division Commander Chen...

402
00:17:14,839 --> 00:17:15,759
...if we win...

403
00:17:16,759 --> 00:17:18,319
...our days ahead will be easier.

404
00:17:18,839 --> 00:17:19,599
So...

405
00:17:20,160 --> 00:17:21,319
...please bear with it a bit.

406
00:17:22,279 --> 00:17:22,799
As for me...

407
00:17:23,519 --> 00:17:24,599
...I'll be in the rear...

408
00:17:24,680 --> 00:17:25,559
...waiting for your triumphant return.

409
00:17:26,119 --> 00:17:27,559
I'll have the celebration wine ready for you.

410
00:17:29,079 --> 00:17:30,640
No matter how round you draw the pie...

411
00:17:30,960 --> 00:17:32,039
...it's better to have something practical.

412
00:17:32,039 --> 00:17:32,440
Right.

413
00:17:32,519 --> 00:17:33,400
Exactly.

414
00:17:34,680 --> 00:17:35,599
Otherwise...

415
00:17:35,880 --> 00:17:36,759
...we won't be alive to eat it.

416
00:17:38,079 --> 00:17:39,359
Three armies in a standoff.

417
00:17:39,640 --> 00:17:41,160
Others looking on will also think...

418
00:17:41,160 --> 00:17:42,519
...we look a bit shabby.

419
00:17:49,039 --> 00:17:49,519
All right

420
00:17:50,319 --> 00:17:52,240
Then I'll take out the best stuff

421
00:17:52,880 --> 00:17:53,559
I've been saving for you

422
00:17:53,680 --> 00:17:54,240
Commander

423
00:17:54,359 --> 00:17:55,839
That is our last trump card

424
00:17:56,160 --> 00:17:57,119
You make it sound so intense

425
00:17:57,559 --> 00:17:58,400
What is it?

426
00:18:01,599 --> 00:18:02,519
A tank

427
00:18:04,680 --> 00:18:05,759
A tank

428
00:18:06,759 --> 00:18:07,960
Can we go take a look?

429
00:18:08,960 --> 00:18:10,000
It's already yours

430
00:18:10,440 --> 00:18:11,079
Look all you want

431
00:18:11,799 --> 00:18:12,359
Jizi

432
00:18:12,680 --> 00:18:13,640
Take Commander Fan there

433
00:18:14,319 --> 00:18:14,640
Let's go

434
00:18:14,880 --> 00:18:15,519
Go, go

435
00:18:16,440 --> 00:18:17,119
This way, please

436
00:18:19,559 --> 00:18:21,359
Are we really just sending those ragtag troops?

437
00:18:22,119 --> 00:18:23,799
They only listen to him, not me

438
00:18:24,039 --> 00:18:25,319
If I don't use them as cannon fodder

439
00:18:25,319 --> 00:18:26,200
what good are they?

440
00:18:26,519 --> 00:18:27,960
If they lose

441
00:18:28,079 --> 00:18:29,079
I won't be heartbroken

442
00:18:30,160 --> 00:18:31,480
And if they win?

443
00:18:32,559 --> 00:18:33,519
Relying on them

444
00:18:33,920 --> 00:18:36,000
to beat the well-equipped Liao Guanguan?

445
00:18:36,359 --> 00:18:37,279
Is that even possible?

446
00:18:39,599 --> 00:18:42,039
But Commander Chen doesn't want to lose this battle

447
00:18:42,359 --> 00:18:44,160
He'll definitely send his strongest troops

448
00:18:44,799 --> 00:18:46,359
We'll just tag along and reap the benefits

449
00:18:50,240 --> 00:18:51,039
This battle

450
00:18:51,720 --> 00:18:53,960
is the perfect chance to take that fool down a peg

451
00:18:55,319 --> 00:18:55,960
Otherwise

452
00:18:56,559 --> 00:18:58,480
he'll really think he's a hero

453
00:18:59,839 --> 00:19:00,799
Staff Officer Huo

454
00:19:01,039 --> 00:19:03,559
The latrines in the camp are all cleaned

455
00:19:05,759 --> 00:19:08,240
Given my friendship with Commander Qin

456
00:19:08,400 --> 00:19:11,000
Commander Qin really ought to be scrubbing with me

457
00:19:11,839 --> 00:19:13,720
I don't want to get covered in filth

458
00:19:14,200 --> 00:19:15,599
I warned you long ago

459
00:19:15,839 --> 00:19:18,640
The higher you climb, the harder you fall

460
00:19:20,480 --> 00:19:22,079
I don't mind if Commander Qin laughs

461
00:19:22,640 --> 00:19:25,119
Even if I, Huo, am scrubbing latrines

462
00:19:25,519 --> 00:19:28,200
I'll scrub my way to being Commander Chen's favorite

463
00:19:29,440 --> 00:19:32,000
Commander Chen is taking me to the alliance banquet

464
00:19:32,279 --> 00:19:33,559
because he knows

465
00:19:33,720 --> 00:19:36,160
that only I can keep Fan Sha'er in check

466
00:19:39,160 --> 00:19:40,799
Shameless boasting

467
00:19:41,359 --> 00:19:43,279
That's just so I can match up

468
00:19:43,279 --> 00:19:44,440
to you, Commander Qin

469
00:19:44,960 --> 00:19:45,839
Commander Qin

470
00:19:45,920 --> 00:19:49,119
you are Commander Chen's elite general

471
00:19:49,720 --> 00:19:51,400
If you and I were to join forces

472
00:19:51,480 --> 00:19:53,279
we'd have both brains and brawn

473
00:19:53,440 --> 00:19:54,480
When that happens

474
00:19:54,480 --> 00:19:56,119
even Commander Chen

475
00:19:56,559 --> 00:19:58,079
could be manipulated a little

476
00:20:02,400 --> 00:20:04,359
The world has certainly changed.

477
00:20:05,160 --> 00:20:08,359
A profiteer like you dares to show off in front of me.

478
00:20:08,799 --> 00:20:09,839
In the past,

479
00:20:10,759 --> 00:20:11,559
I would have shot you

480
00:20:11,559 --> 00:20:12,680
without even blinking an eye.

481
00:20:12,680 --> 00:20:13,599
Do you believe me?

482
00:20:14,119 --> 00:20:15,720
You should never underestimate

483
00:20:15,720 --> 00:20:17,359
a soldier's loyalty.

484
00:20:17,880 --> 00:20:18,720
Loyalty?

485
00:20:20,400 --> 00:20:21,920
Using the military's power

486
00:20:22,279 --> 00:20:24,400
to go to the gentry and merchants

487
00:20:24,640 --> 00:20:26,359
and forcibly collect protection taxes?

488
00:20:26,799 --> 00:20:28,200
Using military personnel

489
00:20:28,400 --> 00:20:30,319
to deliver takeout for hotpot restaurants?

490
00:20:31,000 --> 00:20:32,759
Your residence, Commander Qin,

491
00:20:33,000 --> 00:20:34,720
is even more luxurious than Division Commander Chen's.

492
00:20:34,920 --> 00:20:36,640
Tell me, as a loyal soldier,

493
00:20:36,759 --> 00:20:38,400
shouldn't you hand it over?

494
00:20:39,319 --> 00:20:40,799
Are you threatening me?

495
00:20:42,720 --> 00:20:43,319
I wouldn't dare.

496
00:20:43,839 --> 00:20:45,599
I've only heard rumors.

497
00:20:45,839 --> 00:20:47,079
And there's no evidence anyway.

498
00:20:47,079 --> 00:20:48,200
I wasn't involved.

499
00:20:49,440 --> 00:20:51,480
But that Fan Sha'er...

500
00:20:51,640 --> 00:20:54,559
he has always been Commander Qin's partner.

501
00:20:55,039 --> 00:20:57,079
Fan joined Commander Wei's forces long ago.

502
00:20:57,559 --> 00:20:59,359
Now with the two armies allied,

503
00:20:59,720 --> 00:21:01,559
would he really run to Division Commander Chen

504
00:21:01,720 --> 00:21:02,680
and rat me out?

505
00:21:02,799 --> 00:21:03,880
That's hard to say.

506
00:21:04,359 --> 00:21:05,599
You know as well as I do.

507
00:21:05,759 --> 00:21:08,799
Division Commander Chen has always wanted to recruit that Fan.

508
00:21:09,400 --> 00:21:11,720
This alliance to attack Commander Liao's forces...

509
00:21:12,000 --> 00:21:14,640
the person Commander Wei sent is Commander Fan.

510
00:21:15,680 --> 00:21:16,920
So I think

511
00:21:17,119 --> 00:21:20,319
Division Commander Chen might want to recruit him again.

512
00:21:20,960 --> 00:21:22,279
If he comes over,

513
00:21:22,640 --> 00:21:24,559
he's already a commander himself.

514
00:21:24,920 --> 00:21:26,359
He'd be on equal footing with you.

515
00:21:26,680 --> 00:21:27,599
After he arrives,

516
00:21:27,680 --> 00:21:31,240
do you think Division Commander Chen will promote him?

517
00:21:32,160 --> 00:21:33,279
Once he's promoted,

518
00:21:33,359 --> 00:21:35,119
he'll be walking all over you.

519
00:21:35,440 --> 00:21:37,480
Your life probably won't be easy.

520
00:21:38,400 --> 00:21:40,799
Then if he takes those matters in town,

521
00:21:40,920 --> 00:21:43,279
and spices up the story,

522
00:21:44,920 --> 00:21:45,640
Commander Qin,

523
00:21:46,160 --> 00:21:48,799
you probably won't even be able to keep your underwear.

524
00:21:52,319 --> 00:21:54,559
I assume the Staff Officer has already thought of

525
00:21:54,559 --> 00:21:55,640
a countermeasure for me.

526
00:22:03,039 --> 00:22:04,319
Fan Sha'er

527
00:22:04,519 --> 00:22:06,279
cannot be spared.

528
00:22:06,839 --> 00:22:08,160
So we must seize this opportunity.

529
00:22:08,680 --> 00:22:09,440
Commander Qin,

530
00:22:09,880 --> 00:22:12,640
you must ask Division Commander Chen for battle orders.

531
00:22:13,160 --> 00:22:16,720
On the battlefield, bullets have no eyes.

532
00:22:17,160 --> 00:22:19,119
We can then take the chance...

533
00:22:20,480 --> 00:22:23,920
Killing our own before the allies even march?

534
00:22:24,400 --> 00:22:27,039
I can't take the blame for that.

535
00:22:27,039 --> 00:22:28,200
Commander Qin,

536
00:22:28,599 --> 00:22:30,920
we have always been on the same side.

537
00:22:31,160 --> 00:22:31,880
I guarantee,

538
00:22:32,240 --> 00:22:34,079
I won't let you take the fall.

539
00:22:34,160 --> 00:22:35,039
Furthermore,

540
00:22:35,559 --> 00:22:37,680
I will ensure you get the top credit.

541
00:22:39,240 --> 00:22:40,799
A tank!

542
00:22:41,359 --> 00:22:42,079
It's really a tank!

543
00:22:42,799 --> 00:22:43,680
This is awesome!

544
00:22:43,839 --> 00:22:45,079
Let me go up and try it, Brother.

545
00:22:45,079 --> 00:22:46,559
Alright, alright. Slow down, slow down.

546
00:22:47,640 --> 00:22:49,079
Why is this barrel so thick?

547
00:22:49,880 --> 00:22:50,839
Tank!

548
00:22:50,880 --> 00:22:53,039
It really is a tank!

549
00:22:53,119 --> 00:22:55,200
This tank is indeed a tank.

550
00:22:56,240 --> 00:22:57,920
Except it doesn't move.

551
00:22:59,799 --> 00:23:00,720
Then what's the use of it?

552
00:23:02,279 --> 00:23:03,440
It is indeed useless.

553
00:23:03,680 --> 00:23:04,519
Screw it.

554
00:23:05,839 --> 00:23:06,480
Then Commander Wei...

555
00:23:06,480 --> 00:23:07,880
does he actually want us to win the battle?

556
00:23:09,880 --> 00:23:11,599
He wants to use this battle

557
00:23:12,680 --> 00:23:15,400
to see if we can truly be of use to him.

558
00:23:15,640 --> 00:23:17,759
That bastard Wei is doing this on purpose.

559
00:23:18,400 --> 00:23:19,519
Isn't he afraid we'll rebel?

560
00:23:19,960 --> 00:23:21,000
Let's just rebel and be done with it.

561
00:23:21,000 --> 00:23:21,799
You're right.

562
00:23:22,480 --> 00:23:23,720
Let's rebel. We won't work for him anymore.

563
00:23:23,720 --> 00:23:25,000
We have already formed an alliance.

564
00:23:25,519 --> 00:23:27,000
Stabbing someone in the back...

565
00:23:27,599 --> 00:23:28,440
isn't righteous.

566
00:23:32,880 --> 00:23:33,720
The tank is moving!

567
00:23:34,079 --> 00:23:34,839
The tank is moving!

568
00:23:34,839 --> 00:23:35,920
What is that?

569
00:23:36,480 --> 00:23:37,119
Is it a rat?

570
00:23:39,160 --> 00:23:40,720
Catch it! Catch it! Catch it!

571
00:23:41,319 --> 00:23:42,279
Let's see how big this rat is.

572
00:23:43,400 --> 00:23:43,960
Who are you?

573
00:23:44,319 --> 00:23:45,279
Why did you hit me?

574
00:23:48,440 --> 00:23:49,480
Brother!

575
00:23:49,839 --> 00:23:50,559
Brother!

576
00:23:50,839 --> 00:23:51,839
How come it's you?

577
00:23:56,319 --> 00:23:57,839
There's more food. Eat slowly.

578
00:23:59,119 --> 00:24:00,319
The kid is starving.

579
00:24:00,799 --> 00:24:01,759
Go pour him some water.

580
00:24:03,640 --> 00:24:04,480
Slow down, slow down.

581
00:24:08,039 --> 00:24:09,000
Now,

582
00:24:09,000 --> 00:24:11,319
I formally introduce to everyone,

583
00:24:11,640 --> 00:24:13,680
my sworn little brother.

584
00:24:18,200 --> 00:24:19,799
What's your name?

585
00:24:19,960 --> 00:24:22,200
I forgot to ask when we swore brotherhood last time.

586
00:24:22,640 --> 00:24:24,240
I have already abandoned my name.

587
00:24:24,960 --> 00:24:26,480
A child of the Jianghu wanders the world.

588
00:24:27,240 --> 00:24:29,039
Please give me a new name, Big Brother.

589
00:24:29,640 --> 00:24:32,079
You're the little beggars'

590
00:24:32,400 --> 00:24:33,720
ringleader.

591
00:24:35,200 --> 00:24:37,079
How about we call you Little Boss?

592
00:24:37,759 --> 00:24:38,279
That works.

593
00:24:38,680 --> 00:24:39,799
That name's got a kick to it.

594
00:24:41,039 --> 00:24:43,079
You really do love swearing brotherhood everywhere.

595
00:24:43,319 --> 00:24:44,000
So what?

596
00:24:44,960 --> 00:24:45,799
Everyone sitting here

597
00:24:45,920 --> 00:24:47,839
is a sworn brother of mine.

598
00:24:48,079 --> 00:24:48,759
Except for you.

599
00:24:50,519 --> 00:24:51,680
We went back looking for you, too.

600
00:24:51,759 --> 00:24:52,599
But we couldn't find you.

601
00:24:53,880 --> 00:24:55,000
How did you end up here?

602
00:24:55,079 --> 00:24:56,039
My old man's people

603
00:24:56,279 --> 00:24:57,599
found me in that place.

604
00:24:58,160 --> 00:24:59,680
So naturally, I couldn't stay there anymore.

605
00:25:00,119 --> 00:25:00,680
Enough about that.

606
00:25:03,160 --> 00:25:05,279
You just joined up and you're already a commander.

607
00:25:05,359 --> 00:25:06,519
Not bad.

608
00:25:09,160 --> 00:25:11,000
What were you doing over by the tank?

609
00:25:11,599 --> 00:25:13,319
I stayed there for ages without getting caught.

610
00:25:13,599 --> 00:25:15,079
We're planning to take the tank into battle.

611
00:25:15,680 --> 00:25:16,400
Who are you fighting?

612
00:25:16,680 --> 00:25:17,680
Commander Liao.

613
00:25:18,519 --> 00:25:19,400
Commander Liao?

614
00:25:19,839 --> 00:25:21,359
You want to fight Commander Liao?

615
00:25:22,000 --> 00:25:23,119
What are you laughing at?

616
00:25:23,559 --> 00:25:24,559
You look down on us?

617
00:25:25,440 --> 00:25:26,599
I certainly do look down on you.

618
00:25:26,880 --> 00:25:28,079
Just the few of you?

619
00:25:29,039 --> 00:25:30,680
That's Commander Liao.

620
00:25:31,519 --> 00:25:32,240
See that?

621
00:25:32,440 --> 00:25:34,119
Even a kid can read the situation.

622
00:25:35,359 --> 00:25:36,279
Commander Liao...

623
00:25:36,880 --> 00:25:38,359
is he really that tough?

624
00:25:38,519 --> 00:25:39,640
He's more than just tough.

625
00:25:40,319 --> 00:25:42,160
With those few junk tanks of yours,

626
00:25:43,279 --> 00:25:46,200
you couldn't even scratch the tip of Commander Liao's toe.

627
00:25:46,359 --> 00:25:48,000
Then why the hell are we fighting?

628
00:25:48,240 --> 00:25:49,720
Forget it. We're not fighting.

629
00:25:50,000 --> 00:25:51,400
That won't do.

630
00:25:51,799 --> 00:25:53,839
This is our first battle for Commander Wei.

631
00:25:54,200 --> 00:25:56,319
We can't just back down before we start.

632
00:25:56,680 --> 00:25:58,119
How would we ever show our faces again?

633
00:25:58,319 --> 00:25:59,720
Fighting when you know you'll lose?

634
00:26:00,279 --> 00:26:02,599
Why throw your brothers' lives away?

635
00:26:05,640 --> 00:26:08,400
If you must fight, it's not impossible.

636
00:26:09,160 --> 00:26:10,000
Take me

637
00:26:13,160 --> 00:26:13,920
along with you.

638
00:26:15,359 --> 00:26:16,680
We're fighting a war,

639
00:26:16,799 --> 00:26:18,079
not playing house.

640
00:26:18,559 --> 00:26:20,039
War is about tactics.

641
00:26:20,480 --> 00:26:22,200
Outsmarting the enemy takes strategy.

642
00:26:22,400 --> 00:26:23,599
The Art of War speaks of...

643
00:26:24,720 --> 00:26:26,119
Pre-battle preparations,

644
00:26:26,519 --> 00:26:27,960
the application of strategy,

645
00:26:28,200 --> 00:26:29,799
Look at them, they're totally lost.

646
00:26:30,400 --> 00:26:31,720
and the analysis of enemy intelligence.

647
00:26:32,240 --> 00:26:32,960
About these things,

648
00:26:33,680 --> 00:26:35,519
you probably don't know as much as I do.

649
00:26:37,680 --> 00:26:40,720
You're quite something, Little Boss.

650
00:26:42,160 --> 00:26:43,880
To fight, you must strike their weakness.

651
00:26:44,240 --> 00:26:46,000
To attack, you must hit their vitals.

652
00:26:47,400 --> 00:26:48,079
Do you happen to know

653
00:26:48,079 --> 00:26:49,880
where Commander Liao's armory is?

654
00:26:52,759 --> 00:26:54,079
Or where his granary is?

655
00:26:56,640 --> 00:26:57,920
How do you know that?

656
00:26:59,039 --> 00:27:01,200
With the sky for a blanket and the earth for a bed,

657
00:27:01,400 --> 00:27:02,920
I crawl around everywhere, all day long.

658
00:27:03,759 --> 00:27:05,599
I even found your junk tanks, didn't I?

659
00:27:06,359 --> 00:27:07,759
Is there anything I can't find?

660
00:27:08,279 --> 00:27:09,400
Boss, have some water.

661
00:27:09,400 --> 00:27:10,319
Here, have some chicken. Eat up.

662
00:27:10,319 --> 00:27:11,799
Let me pour you another bowl of water.

663
00:27:18,079 --> 00:27:20,440
You really do know everything.

664
00:27:21,000 --> 00:27:21,759
Take me with you.

665
00:27:22,440 --> 00:27:23,480
Even if we can't topple Commander Liao,

666
00:27:23,920 --> 00:27:25,039
we can at least make him hurt.

667
00:27:26,599 --> 00:27:27,279
Good.

668
00:27:28,759 --> 00:27:30,799
This is a battle we have to fight.

669
00:27:31,400 --> 00:27:33,720
The conditions are harsh and difficulties abound.

670
00:27:35,000 --> 00:27:35,640
However,

671
00:27:36,519 --> 00:27:37,920
we have allies.

672
00:27:38,839 --> 00:27:41,279
If worst comes to worst, the allies go first.

673
00:27:41,920 --> 00:27:43,519
We'll just hide behind their butts.

674
00:27:44,440 --> 00:27:45,039
Exactly.

675
00:27:45,519 --> 00:27:46,839
If we win this battle,

676
00:27:47,039 --> 00:27:48,359
I'll go ask the Commander for a reward.

677
00:27:48,799 --> 00:27:50,519
Even if we lose, it's no big deal.

678
00:27:50,839 --> 00:27:52,799
I'll just go and explain it nicely to the Commander.

679
00:27:53,039 --> 00:27:53,920
None of this is important.

680
00:27:54,319 --> 00:27:55,200
What's most important is,

681
00:27:55,799 --> 00:27:56,720
on the battlefield,

682
00:27:56,960 --> 00:27:58,720
everyone must focus on staying alive.

683
00:27:59,559 --> 00:28:01,119
Coming back safely

684
00:28:01,200 --> 00:28:02,880
is the greatest victory.

685
00:28:03,559 --> 00:28:06,279
This time we're allying with Wei's forces to attack Liao's forces.

686
00:28:07,160 --> 00:28:08,279
How do you all think

687
00:28:09,000 --> 00:28:09,960
this battle should be fought?

688
00:28:10,200 --> 00:28:11,480
Since there are allies,

689
00:28:11,839 --> 00:28:13,160
let the allies charge in front.

690
00:28:13,519 --> 00:28:15,240
Let's not make senseless sacrifices.

691
00:28:15,480 --> 00:28:16,240
Preserve our strength,

692
00:28:16,680 --> 00:28:17,759
and pick up the spoils later.

693
00:28:18,039 --> 00:28:18,960
If you think like that,

694
00:28:19,440 --> 00:28:20,400
the other side thinks like that too.

695
00:28:20,599 --> 00:28:21,440
Then this battle,

696
00:28:21,839 --> 00:28:22,640
what's the point of fighting it?

697
00:28:23,039 --> 00:28:25,240
I think, since we are an alliance,

698
00:28:25,680 --> 00:28:27,759
we should follow the rules of the pact.

699
00:28:28,279 --> 00:28:29,400
We show our strength,

700
00:28:29,680 --> 00:28:30,759
and together with our allies,

701
00:28:31,160 --> 00:28:33,279
if we fight, we fight to our heart's content.

702
00:28:38,400 --> 00:28:39,680
War,

703
00:28:40,200 --> 00:28:43,039
originally has no black and white, right or wrong.

704
00:28:43,440 --> 00:28:45,279
To put it plainly, it's all a struggle for benefits.

705
00:28:45,880 --> 00:28:46,960
Since we are fighting,

706
00:28:47,319 --> 00:28:49,720
we must find a way to maximize our benefits.

707
00:28:52,119 --> 00:28:53,839
Allies are allies,

708
00:28:54,519 --> 00:28:55,960
but we can't hang our heads

709
00:28:55,960 --> 00:28:57,559
on someone else's body.

710
00:28:58,200 --> 00:28:59,960
We must fight side by side with the allies,

711
00:29:00,279 --> 00:29:02,079
and create opportunities for them,

712
00:29:02,839 --> 00:29:03,880
build ladders for them,

713
00:29:04,200 --> 00:29:05,440
help them ram the city gates,

714
00:29:05,799 --> 00:29:07,839
and let them achieve victory.

715
00:29:09,240 --> 00:29:10,559
Then where does the benefit come from?

716
00:29:11,759 --> 00:29:12,400
Well,

717
00:29:13,559 --> 00:29:16,240
allies becoming enemies

718
00:29:17,119 --> 00:29:19,000
happens in a split second.

719
00:29:20,880 --> 00:29:22,359
Just after fighting Commander Liao,

720
00:29:22,880 --> 00:29:23,960
we and the allies

721
00:29:24,200 --> 00:29:26,720
will inevitably suffer casualties.

722
00:29:27,599 --> 00:29:29,039
To go to war with the allies again,

723
00:29:29,519 --> 00:29:31,480
do you think we can afford that?

724
00:29:31,480 --> 00:29:34,079
The allies sent a bandit squad.

725
00:29:34,319 --> 00:29:35,039
Gentlemen,

726
00:29:35,480 --> 00:29:37,200
we are wearing military uniforms.

727
00:29:37,759 --> 00:29:39,839
You make it sound so easy.

728
00:29:40,079 --> 00:29:41,319
If we do it your way,

729
00:29:41,599 --> 00:29:43,279
who would dare ally with us in the future?

730
00:29:44,240 --> 00:29:46,839
Winners are kings, losers are bandits.

731
00:29:47,240 --> 00:29:49,599
History is written by the survivors.

732
00:29:50,799 --> 00:29:51,839
Gentlemen, please look.

733
00:29:52,200 --> 00:29:53,400
Secret order from Wei's headquarters.

734
00:29:57,359 --> 00:29:57,920
Urgent order:

735
00:29:58,000 --> 00:30:01,319
After Commander Fan and Chen's army finish attacking Liao's troops,

736
00:30:01,440 --> 00:30:05,160
immediately execute the Chen army generals on the spot.

737
00:30:06,160 --> 00:30:07,319
This is a secret order.

738
00:30:08,559 --> 00:30:09,119
Commander.

739
00:30:14,960 --> 00:30:16,039
So,

740
00:30:16,799 --> 00:30:19,039
they were the ones who broke faith first.

741
00:30:20,359 --> 00:30:21,839
At most, ours counts as...

742
00:30:22,039 --> 00:30:22,839
Counts as, counts as...

743
00:30:23,079 --> 00:30:25,039
counts as justifiable defense.

744
00:30:26,599 --> 00:30:27,119
Wicked.

745
00:30:28,440 --> 00:30:29,640
Too wicked.

746
00:30:31,400 --> 00:30:32,480
However,

747
00:30:33,720 --> 00:30:34,720
I like it.

748
00:30:36,160 --> 00:30:36,799
Commander.

749
00:30:37,200 --> 00:30:39,160
I am willing to lead the troops

750
00:30:39,319 --> 00:30:41,319
and complete this arduous task.

751
00:30:42,400 --> 00:30:44,480
No rush, no rush.

752
00:30:46,160 --> 00:30:47,319
I am a greedy man.

753
00:30:48,039 --> 00:30:49,799
I want one more thing.

754
00:30:50,079 --> 00:30:51,240
Please enlighten us, Commander.

755
00:30:53,680 --> 00:30:55,440
The regimental commander sent by the allies this time

756
00:30:55,720 --> 00:30:56,880
is a bandit leader,

757
00:30:57,400 --> 00:30:59,279
and also the hero who killed the Japanese,

758
00:30:59,400 --> 00:31:00,720
Fan Pengju.

759
00:31:01,200 --> 00:31:02,119
He is a talent.

760
00:31:03,039 --> 00:31:04,240
Everyone knows I cherish talent.

761
00:31:05,519 --> 00:31:06,559
Sending you...

762
00:31:07,039 --> 00:31:08,920
would that make things difficult for you?

763
00:31:09,400 --> 00:31:10,000
Well...

764
00:31:10,200 --> 00:31:10,839
Division Commander Chen,

765
00:31:11,960 --> 00:31:13,920
Commander Qin came up with the strategy.

766
00:31:14,039 --> 00:31:17,319
So it is most appropriate for Commander Qin to lead the troops.

767
00:31:18,000 --> 00:31:18,920
And I believe,

768
00:31:18,920 --> 00:31:20,960
Commander Qin is a man who sees the big picture.

769
00:31:21,559 --> 00:31:23,799
I am willing to accompany Commander Qin

770
00:31:23,960 --> 00:31:25,039
and lend a helping hand.

771
00:31:25,440 --> 00:31:26,920
Do you two take me for a fool?

772
00:31:28,640 --> 00:31:30,319
Think I don't know you're settling private scores?

773
00:31:31,359 --> 00:31:33,039
Haven't you scrubbed enough toilets?

774
00:31:33,720 --> 00:31:35,279
That is exactly why I must go.

775
00:31:36,000 --> 00:31:38,279
Serving as a staff officer under Division Commander Chen,

776
00:31:38,680 --> 00:31:40,160
one must act like a staff officer.

777
00:31:40,519 --> 00:31:42,160
So I want to take this opportunity

778
00:31:42,480 --> 00:31:43,640
to correct my previous mistakes.

779
00:31:44,039 --> 00:31:45,000
To let everyone know,

780
00:31:45,000 --> 00:31:46,559
when it comes to Division Commander Chen's interests,

781
00:31:46,799 --> 00:31:49,599
my personal grievances are trivial.

782
00:31:51,359 --> 00:31:52,480
So, Commander Qin,

783
00:31:53,079 --> 00:31:54,759
are you willing to sign a military pledge?

784
00:31:55,480 --> 00:31:56,759
A military pledge?

785
00:32:05,400 --> 00:32:06,079
Commander,

786
00:32:06,279 --> 00:32:07,839
I am willing to sign a military pledge.

787
00:32:08,480 --> 00:32:09,680
In accordance with your instructions,

788
00:32:10,160 --> 00:32:11,000
to complete the mission.
